A map trikz Developed by the Developing Trust Team. There are 16 levels (8 easy and 8 hards) adn the particularity of this map is that the level change after the first jump completed. Thus, the second jumper have to jump as well. At the end of the map, there is a counter to know how many bunny jump you can do in a row. Enjoy
